 arg‚Üźopts Center arg;from;actions;units;‚ąÜwhere;‚ąÜsize;‚ąÜextent;where;parent;stretch;psize;pscale;punits;extent;Borders;where_extent;border;_size;size
‚ćĚ Generic routine to auto-center new objects on their parent by modifying the provided argument list before ‚ąÜWI execution
‚ćĚ opts‚Üź namespace with optional controlling variables
‚ćĚ       parent: reference to parent object [required]
‚ćĚ       stretch: pretend new object is this many pixels bigger (vertical, horizontal) for centering calculations
‚ćĚ If this routine is not used during ‚ąáNew processing, be sure to at least set _where, _extent, & _size variables before calling ‚ąáInitialize.

 from‚Üź‚äÉ‚éēRSI ‚ćĚ Immediate source namespace calling me (where I can find settings)
